def set_end_line_num(
    self, line_num: int
) -> Union[
    "BaseModelBuilder",
    "ModuleModelBuilder",
    "ClassModelBuilder",
    "FunctionModelBuilder",
]:
    """Sets the end line number of the code block model instance."""
    self.common_attributes.end_line_num = line_num
    return self
